r when it captured the <LOCATION> West </LOCATION> <LOCATION> Bank </LOCATION> from <LOCATION> Jordan </LOCATION> and the <LOCATION> Gaza </LOCATION> <LOCATION> Strip </LOCATION> from <LOCATION> Egypt </LOCATION>. <PERSON> Shamir </PERSON> has pledged never to return to the pre-1967 borders. The nearly 10-month-old Palestinian revolt against <LOCATION> Israeli </LOCATION> rule is the top issue in the tight election campaign. More than 280 Arabs and six Israelis have been killed in the violence, which erupted Dec. 8. Both parties oppose creation of an independent Palestinian state.
