<SECOND>AM-Myerson Trial,0324</SECOND>
<HEAD>Myerson Trial: Law Clerk's Testimony Continues</HEAD>
<BYLINE>By JOHN M. DOYLE</BYLINE>
<BYLINE>Associated Press Writer</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>NEW YORK (AP) </DATELINE>
