reement with another company. `` I wonder how Apple, <ORGANIZATION> Compaq </ORGANIZATION>, <ORGANIZATION> Olivetti </ORGANIZATION> are going to feel about this new arrangement,'' <PERSON> Monosson </PERSON> said. `` This is the first product that they are offering to distribute through their sales operation.''
